{"tid":926034,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一個人出世健健康康既機率係幾多","createTime":"2018-12-03T07:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T16:56:51.000Z","uid":151865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bba2b194ada3fa90d1ce085afa25c115525766be","tid":926034,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"先唔講你家庭環境 有無錢個d<br />\n<br />\n到底一個人正正常常有手有腳 無咩先天糖尿病無手無腳又兔唇又K型既機會率係幾多？<br />\n<br />\n雖然每種先天缺陷都係萬分之幾機會，或者千分之機 但世界上有咁多先天缺陷 你要避過曬咁多種 就唔係咁容易 有無人知一個人出世健健康康既機率係幾多？數學既角度係咪要1-曬世界上咁多種先天缺陷同疾病既機率？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有時咁諗 真係覺得自己咁健康已經好好彩好幸福 有無大神解答到"},{"pid":"1036e7891efdea2a71b9bf4ed58c803c7088f86f","tid":926034,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"一個人生得毒嘅機率係幾多？我唔通係地獄黑仔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a200a6b1a749e884b85ec5649ad6a385dcd21b","tid":926034,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1036e7891efdea2a71b9bf4ed58c803c7088f86f","tid":926034,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"一個人生得毒嘅機率係幾多？我唔通係地獄黑仔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"心態決定境界"},{"pid":"e04f6c1998be260a7a1de640836c14c4635fe928","tid":926034,"uid":123323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"先天完美又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n病嘅嘢，後天影響仲大"},{"pid":"6d35ed13db968746810575c2c459e74ab30caedd","tid":926034,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e04f6c1998be260a7a1de640836c14c4635fe928","tid":926034,"uid":123323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"先天完美又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n病嘅嘢，後天影響仲大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03